{"tid":1640053,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"必須要有個訊息帶比藍絲係「犯我者雖遠必誅」","createTime":"2019-10-08T23:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T00:38:53.000Z","uid":118132,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb19e1033d1f16a1e12e682586f326a9cfe2ea8d","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:34:36.000Z","msg":"對家已經正式係群眾鬥群眾一戰中率先響起戰鼓<br />\n撞斷手足對腳都可以安然無恙咁係醫院訓一晚然後出院<br />\n相反手足腳又斷左仲要被控暴動罪<br />\n而犯案者仲要大搖大擺咁拎幾十萬獎勵<br />\n依度我唔係想批評當日阻止繼續行私刑嘅左膠<br />\n而係要認真咁同大家講<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咁嘅悲劇只會愈來愈多</span></span></strong><br />\n今次個司機係必須搵機會執多一劑<br />\n而若果再有下次藍絲意圖想咁做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各位毋需手軟</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關節同下體</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">左膠者同罪</span></span></strong><br />\n你唔忍心落手可以去睇水<br />\n可以幫架車裝修<br />\n甚至乎拿拿聲走人<br />\n唔好令件事再一次再一次咁不斷發生"},{"pid":"f84fab23f9b1b1ac3dc0135f2d584a6adcd24874","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"174bac7e8dc8ff94d485b1d0b5f7a7d1123ffb77","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:35:37.000Z","msg":"2/20"},{"pid":"56c331dffa1bbfa179fa5fb257fbb3d52b58af2c","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:35:50.000Z","msg":"3/20"},{"pid":"af47b4b820da03058b91457c10691cf84319f2aa","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:36:00.000Z","msg":"4/20"},{"pid":"70de2ec85f2f2bdc4585673ab637f7691a06ac7f","tid":1640053,"uid":118132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T23:36:13.000Z","msg":"5/20"},{"pid":"072431e0ffc69a993fd1acdfa15d1d76a751c421","